## Rules

All documentation must be written in English. This includes:

1. README.md and other Markdown files
2. JSDoc comments in code
3. Code comments
4. Function and variable names
5. Error messages

For consistency and to ensure the project is accessible to a global audience, all documentation and code comments should be in English. This makes the project more maintainable and easier to collaborate on.
